{"tid":500363,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術撚][連住尼]求加latex按鈕","createTime":"2017-12-15T16:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T02:05:19.000Z","uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e773469082be17d8bc7ee1c09df76a888b4e0e19","tid":500363,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"連住尼，可唔可以係出post個到加粒制比我地打latex code呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如係咁<br />\n[latex]<span style=\"color: red;\">XXX</span>[/latex]<br />\n<br />\n就會自動變<br />\n<br />\n[i<strong></strong>mg<strong></strong>]htt<strong></strong>p:/<strong></strong>/ww<strong></strong>w.sciweave<strong></strong>rs<strong></strong>.<strong></strong>o<strong></strong>rg/tex2i<strong></strong>mg<strong></strong>.<strong></strong>ph<strong></strong>p?eq=<span style=\"color: blue;\">XXX</span>&amp;bc=White&amp;fc=Black&amp;im=png&amp;fs=12&amp;ff=arev&amp;edit=0[/im<strong></strong>g]<br />\n<br />\n呢個<span style=\"color: blue;\">XXX</span>係encodeURIComponent(<span style=\"color: red;\">XXX</span>)<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n[latex]\\sum_{k=1}^n (k)=1+2+3...+n=\\frac{(1+n)(n)}{2}[/latex]<br />\npreview個到會出<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sciweavers.org/tex2img.php?eq=%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5En%20%28k%29%3D1%2B2%2B3...%2Bn%3D%5Cfrac%7B%281%2Bn%29%28n%29%7D%7B2%7D&amp;bc=White&amp;fc=Black&amp;im=png&amp;fs=12&amp;ff=arev&amp;edit=0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciweavers.org%2Ftex2img.php%3Feq%3D%255Csum_%257Bk%253D1%257D%255En%2520%2528k%2529%253D1%252B2%252B3...%252Bn%253D%255Cfrac%257B%25281%252Bn%2529%2528n%2529%257D%257B2%257D%26bc%3DWhite%26fc%3DBlack%26im%3Dpng%26fs%3D12%26ff%3Darev%26edit%3D0&h=afb47fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S.  上面img 段code係有encode到，但係preview有bug整走左啲encode (%2B轉左做＋)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳細在此：<a href=\"http://www.sciweavers.org/free-online-la